name: Compound Coin
public_notice: This coin is not related to Compound.Finance. To see Compound Governance Token, see: https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/compound-governance-token

description.en:
Building Bridges
Compound Coin was born out of the death of UKC coin. The original developers of Compound coin offered fair 1-1 swap of UKC coin to COMP coin. This enabled those with coins of now no value to swap them for a new and working coin.

Coin Swap
The initial COMP premine was used for a swap from UKC to COMP and for development. Unused coins were burned – The total burned coins amount to over 550 million at the moment.
